"I was done with it the minute I saw it!" (Master Shake from ATHF, about Redbook magazine, in the waiting-room-like interior of the Plutonian's melting machine)

These are getting a bit obscure ;)

4/N

"IT'S NOT WORKING, BUTT-HEAD" (Beavis, trying to look at girls in the reflection of a window, but all he can see is Butt-Head) ... whenever something, like, isn't working. Hehehmhmhm.

3/N

"I *know* how to have sex" (Amy from Futurama, to Bender, when trying to use a claw machine & he was trying to give her tips), whenever we're trying to describe, or hear a description of, complicated instructions.

(usually truncated as "I *know* how to...")

2/N
